      "rdfs:label": "Boundary",
      "rdfs:comment": "A positional marker within inline content used to define the boundary of a cross-block range. Boundaries are referenced by their `id` from other nodes (e.g. `Comment.startLocation` and `Comment.endLocation`) to delimit regions that may span across multiple blocks.",
